headline: How Investors May Respond To Home Depot (HD) Expanding Canadian Same-Day Delivery Via New Instacart Partnership
summary: In early December 2025, Instacart announced a partnership with The Home Depot Canada to provide same-day delivery, often within an hour, from more than 175 stores nationwide, including heavy items up to 60 pounds, just in time for the peak holiday and project season. This move makes The Home Depot Canada the first home improvement chain available nationwide on Instacart in the country, potentially deepening its reach with both DIY customers and Pros who value fast delivery for bulky...
